### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@academyId = PIp0OwatTywTYtbwgccpkmo51HuXoqFq

###############################################
# ALUMNOS - CRUD + QR
###############################################
# Prefix: /api/academies/:academyId/students
# Requiere: sesion activa + pertenecer a la academia
# Primero haz login en auth.http
###############################################

### ========================================
### LISTAR
### ========================================

### Listar alumnos (pagina 1, 20 por pagina)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/academies/{{academyId}}/students?page=1&pageSize=20

### Listar con busqueda por nombre
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/academies/{{academyId}}/students?search=juan&page=1&pageSize=10

### Pagina 2
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/academies/{{academyId}}/students?page=2&pageSize=5

### ========================================
### CREAR
### ========================================

### Crear alumno completo
# @name createStudent
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/academies/{{academyId}}/students
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Alvaro Solis",
  "email": "alvaro.solis@email.com",
  "phone": "9992333450"
}

### Crear alumno solo con campos requeridos
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/academies/{{academyId}}/students
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Ana Martinez",
  "email": "ana.martinez@email.com"
}

### Crear alumno - sin email (debe fallar)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/academies/{{academyId}}/students
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Sin Email"
}

### ========================================
### OBTENER POR ID
### ========================================

@studentId = c89f49f9-8ea6-4416-a6c3-cefc2184c4ab

### Obtener alumno por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/academies/{{academyId}}/students/{{studentId}}

### ========================================
### ACTUALIZAR
### ========================================

### Actualizar alumno (campos parciales)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/academies/{{academyId}}/students/{{studentId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "+52 55 3333 4444"
}

### Desactivar alumno
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/academies/{{academyId}}/students/{{studentId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "is_active": false
}

### ========================================
### ELIMINAR
### ========================================

### Eliminar alumno
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/academies/{{academyId}}/students/{{studentId}}

### ========================================
### HISTORIAL DE GRUPOS DEL ALUMNO
### ========================================

### Grupos en los que esta/estuvo inscrito
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/academies/{{academyId}}/students/{{studentId}}/groups

### ========================================
### HISTORIAL DE PAGOS DEL ALUMNO
### ========================================

### Pagos del alumno
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/academies/{{academyId}}/students/{{studentId}}/payments

### ========================================
### CODIGO QR
### ========================================

### Obtener o generar QR del alumno
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/academies/{{academyId}}/students/{{studentId}}/qr
